About Me

Hello! I'm Akif, a cybersecurity enthusiast student at the University of South Florida and a former Security Analyst Trainee at ReliaQuest. My global living experiences have shaped my adaptability and communication skills, equipping me to tackle challenges head-on. Off the clock, I'm either sharpening my skills on the soccer field or sharing my fitness journey on YouTube.

My Experience

- ReliaQuest: Engaged in hands-on cybersecurity operations, learning and applying real-world security solutions.
- University of South Florida (USF): My academic tenure here broadened my technical and theoretical understanding, preparing me for the complex world of IT security.

My YouTube Journey

Catch a glimpse of my passion for soccer and my exploration into cybersecurity through my YouTube channel:

I love using TryHackMe in my spare time to delve into the core principles of cybersecurity, constantly learning and evolving.

Future Aspirations

I'm at the beginning stages of building this website to not only showcase my HomeLab progress but to also share upcoming learning and professional experiences. Stay tuned for a thrilling ride into the future of technology and personal growth!
